58. Construct a PHP program to extract the mail addresses in the given
string using regular expression.
<?php
// Input string with multiple emails
$text = "Please contact us at support@example.com, sales@test.org or info@company.co.in.";

// Regular Expression for email addresses
$pattern = "/[a-zA-Z0-9._%+-]+@[a-zA-Z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,}/";

// Find all matches
preg_match_all($pattern, $text, $matches);

// Display extracted email addresses
echo "Extracted Email Addresses:\n";
print_r($matches[0]);
?>
output:
Extracted Email Addresses:
Array
(
    [0] => support@example.com
    [1] => sales@test.org
    [2] => info@company.co.in
)
